This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4102

Inspired by vim-rails this plugin makes navigating through your brunch (http://brunch.io) projects a lot more comfortable. Besides an interface to the brunch command line it offers ex commands to quickly move from one brunch file to one of its related files.

Want to open your user model? Type :Bmodel user. Need the corresponding unit test in a vertical split? Just go :BVtest.

Grab the latest dev version from github: https://github.com/drichard/vim-brunch
